<p style="padding-left:5px;">1. Any Fule Kno That (4:27)<br>2. Almost Human (4:23)<br>3. Don't Make Me Happy (4:55)<br>4. Seventh Heaven (5:22)<br>5. Watching the Sky (5:22)<br>6. Fingers to the Bone (4:45)<br>7. Jack Ruby (3:47)<br>8. She Was (4:16)<br>9. Whatsername (4:26)<br>10. '69 (4:57)<br>11. Evil Louie (4:53)<br>12. Bludsucker (4:27)<br><br>Total Time 56:00</p>

<strong>Line-up / Musicians</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">- Ian Gillan / lead vocals, harmonica<br>- Steve Morse / guitar<br>- Jon Lord / organ, keyboards<br>- Roger Glover / bass<br>- Ian Paice / drums</p>

